WRITING.TITLE: PsBattle: An origami crow on a class desk

WRITING.TEXT: Do you by any chance have any measurements or sketches of the plan for some of us that want to do something really similar. If not could you at least share the overall length, height and width?

3 intake fans in front, 2 exhaust on one side and 2 on the back... Aiming for a bit of a negative pressure... I don't see how a positive pressure would help me as there will not be that many gaps without a fan where the air could escape trough.
The combo hub is a great idea I hope i'll find one with a couple of usb 3.0 ports like my motherboard.
